Ctrl + C            :: Copy
Ctrl + X            :: Cut
Ctrl + V            :: Paste
(Double tap) Ctrl   :: Run anything
Ctrl + /            :: Comment line(s) out
Ctrl + shift + /    :: Comment selected out
Ctrl + Alt + L      :: Auto - indent code
Shift + F6          :: Rename
Ctrl + F            :: Find in window
Ctrl + Shift + F    :: Find in project


